      "canonical_source": "designs/provincial/mass_battle_v30.md",
      "section": "§A.3 Troop count",
      "quoted_text": "1 Size = block_size soldiers",
      "notes": "HP = TroopCount = Size × BLOCK_SIZE. Company scale: Size 4 unit = 400 HP. Pre-existing constant; ledgered in Step 4.2 because LETHALITY_SCALE calibration depends on the HP scale this constant produces."
